05:35.300 --> 05:39.000
Yeah Henry! Come on Henry, let's go!

05:36.500 --> 05:39.000
-Yeah!

05:40.000 --> 05:42.000
Oh my gosh!

05:41.700 --> 05:43.700
I can't believe they're letting him play!

05:43.700 --> 05:48.000
Hustle on into the tunnel, and I don't wanna
