06:12.500 --> 06:14.000
-I got it!

06:13.000 --> 06:15.000
-Go back!

06:15.500 --> 06:17.000
I got it!

06:16.500 --> 06:19.000
-Come on!
-You can catch it!

06:17.500 --> 06:19.000
-I got it!

06:19.000 --> 06:22.000
Oh! 
[heavy breathing]

06:22.000 --> 06:24.000
Get it, get it!

06:25.000 --> 06:27.000
Heh? Huh! Come on!

06:27.000 --> 06:29.000
[heavy breathing]

