Is that play legal?

06:51.500 --> 06:55.000
-Hey.
-Hey.

06:56.000 --> 06:59.000
-How was game?
-[indistinct grunt]

06:59.000 --> 07:02.000
Well, what does that mean?
Did you get to play?

07:01.500 --> 07:04.000
-They put me in right field.

07:04.000 --> 07:07.000
-So how'd you do?
-Let's just say I made the play of the day.

