-In my dreams.

07:20.000 --> 07:22.000
Hey, hey!

07:22.500 --> 07:25.000
-Laundry.
-[sigh] Mom.

07:25.000 --> 07:27.000
-(imitating) Mom.

07:35.000 --> 07:37.000
