07:43.500 --> 07:46.500
What's this?

07:46.500 --> 07:50.000
The Cubs are bringing in their right fielder to pitch?
[imitates cheering]

07:50.500 --> 07:58.000
(echoing) Henry Rowengartner! The entire season is
resting on Rowengartner's shoulders!

07:58.500 --> 08:05.000
Bottom nine. Two out. One on. Full count.

08:05.000 --> 08:09.000
Rowengartner takes a long look at the runner at second.

08:10.500 --> 08:13.000
[thud]
Strike one!

08:16.000 --> 08:20.000
-Honey, dinner's almost ready.
-You're going out again?

08:20.000 --> 08:23.000
Yeah.
You gonna be okay?

08:23.000 --> 08:28.000
-[sigh] What's the occasion?
-It's our three week anniversary.

08:28.000 --> 08:30.500
Three weeks? congratulations.

08:30.500 --> 08:33.500
-(background) Hello? Anyone there? Mary?
-What have you got against Jack?

08:33.500 --> 08:35.000
He's moving too fast!

08:35.000 --> 08:37.000
-Shh.
-Henry! Hey!

08:37.000 --> 08:43.000
Now the three week anniversary is the, um...
That's the necklace anniversary.

08:44.000 --> 08:47.000
Oh, Jack! Uh... (laughs)

08:48.000 --> 08:51.500
-Oh, Jack, this, uh...
-Let me get that on you.

08:51.500 --> 08:54.000
This is too much.

08:54.000 --> 08:57.000
-[sigh]
-[kissing noises]

08:57.500 --> 09:03.000
