Okay, uh, honey? In bed by 8:30
and do all your homework. 

09:10.000 --> 09:13.000
-[kiss]
-[imitates buzzer]

09:13.700 --> 09:18.000
-You're gonna love this restaurant, Mary.
-[door closes]

09:22.500 --> 09:26.000
-I think Henry is really starting to like me!
-Um, yeah.

09:26.000 --> 09:33.000
